UPDATED: NOV 28, 2011 AROMA: Malty ( toast and nuts) and slightly ripe fruit (bananas and oranges);
APPEARANCE: Clear, deep orange and gold brown, thin head with persistent lacing;
TASTE: medium sweetness, very slightly bitter;
PALATE: Big body, creamy, slightly astringent and sour finish, effervescent; 
OVERALL: Big and robust
